---
export const prerender = true;

import FinalEngagement from '../../components/final-engagement.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/icon.astro';
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/main-layout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/hero-section.astro';
import HeroEngagement from '../../components/hero-engagement.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Legacy System Modernization"
  description="Transform outdated systems into modern, scalable solutions. Our legacy system modernization services ensure your business is equipped for future growth with secure, efficient technologies."
  keywords="legacy system modernization, future-proof systems, modern tech stack, migrate legacy applications, secure web solutions, scalable web platforms"
>
  <link rel="preload" href="/images/services/legacy-system.webp" as="image" type="image/webp" slot="html-head" />
  <HeroSection image="services/legacy-system">
    <p class="heading1 inverted">Upgrade Your Legacy Systems to Future-Ready Solutions</p>
    <p class="text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
      Don't let outdated technology hold your business back—modernize and scale without disruption.
    </p>
    <HeroEngagement />
  </HeroSection>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <header>
        <p class="tagline">Future-Proof Your Business</p>
        <h1 class="heading2">Legacy System Modernization Services</h1>
      </header>
      <div class="even-columns slim-content one-column">
        <p class="body1 text-center text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
          Our Legacy System Modernization Services upgrade antiquated software and infrastructure to better serve in
          terms of improved performance, security, and scalability. Mueller transforms legacy applications into new
          cloud-based systems that allow current new technologies to be incorporated while significantly enhancing user
          experiences with little disruption in currently running operations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section gradient-up">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <header>
        <p class="tagline">Outdated Systems Are Costing You — Here's How to Fix It</p>
        <h2 class="heading2">Why You Need Legacy System Modernization</h2>
      </header>
      <ul class="even-columns three-columns">
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="choice" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Future-Proof Your Business</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Transition to modern tech stacks for long-term sustainability.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="rocket" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Boost Efficiency</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Upgrade to faster, more efficient platforms that cut operational costs.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="check" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Improve Security</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Eliminate vulnerabilities by using secure, modern frameworks.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="net" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Seamless Integration</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Integrate easily with new tools and systems to stay competitive.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="strategies" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Scalability</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Ensure your system is built to scale as your business grows.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <Icon name="proof" width="68" height="68" />
          <h3 class="heading3">Enhanced User Experience</h3>
          <p class="body2 text-balance text-pretty-mobile">
            Provide a smoother, more intuitive experience with modern interfaces.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section primary">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <header>
        <p class="tagline inverted">Transform Your Business — One Update at a Time</p>
        <h2 class="heading2 inverted">The Business Case for Modernization</h2>
      </header>
      <ul class="even-columns four-columns">
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <strong class="heading1 text-bold">60%</strong>
          <span class="body2 text-balance">
            of businesses experience increased productivity after system modernization.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <strong class="heading1 text-bold">90%</strong>
          <span class="body2 text-balance"> of breaches are caused by outdated software in legacy systems. </span>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <strong class="heading1 text-bold">30%</strong>
          <span class="body2 text-balance"> reduction in operational costs is seen with modernized platforms. </span>
        </li>
        <li class="card white shadow align-center fade-from-bottom">
          <strong class="heading1 text-bold">50%</strong>
          <span class="body2 text-balance">
            improvement in user experience is reported by businesses with upgraded systems.
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section wrapper">
    <header>
      <p class="tagline">A Modernization Process That Works</p>
      <h2 class="heading2">Our Step-by-Step Legacy System Modernization Process</h2>
    </header>
    <ul class="even-columns two-columns slim-content">
      <li class="card blue align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">System Assessment</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          An assessment has been done of your existing legacy system not only architecture but also performance and
          constraints it imposes upon you. This helps us understand not just what the system does but what it needs to
          do to meet your business needs in those requirements evolutions.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card red align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Strategic Planning</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          Whether enriching the performance of your system, optimizing user experiences, or preparing for the future, we
          will assist you in ordering initiatives based on their business benefits against feasibility.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card purple align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Tech Stack Upgrade</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          We will check any third-party software or platforms that your legacy system interacts with, at this time so we
          can ensure compatibility with a new stack.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card green align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Data & Functionality Migration</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          We do this with the utmost care, mapping legacy functions into their modern counterparts in order not to lose
          any essential features or capabilities during the transition. Our team works diligently to ensure as little
          downtime as possible and to have your operations continue with minimal disruption.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card blue align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Rigorous Testing</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          Our dedicated QA teams collaborate with your team in validating functionality, security, and scalability for
          the new system, after which it identifies any bugs or issues. After discovery, the new system was fixed and
          made robust and reliable.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card purple align-left fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Ongoing Support</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          We're here to provide continuous improvement and ensure that your system is current with growing businesses
          and emerging technology, that is, as the traffic of your system increases, new features are requested for
          addition to the system, or when updated regulations demand you to be compliant with the changes.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="section wrapper">
    <header>
      <p class="tagline">Got Questions? We've Got Answers.</p>
      <h2 class="heading2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </header>
    <ul class="even-columns slim-content one-column">
      <li class="card white shadow fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">Why should my business modernize its legacy system?</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          With the older, higher-maintenance, rigid, and insecure systems replaced with the modern ones, one can easily
          employ AI, Cloud technology, and Data analysis to spur transformation through innovation.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card white shadow fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">How long does the legacy system modernization process take?</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          We work in a manner that there is no disturbance in your business, and the transition is carried out in the
          shortest period without disturbance.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card white shadow fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">How do you ensure that the new system will integrate with our existing technology?</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          We carefully ensure seamless integration of the new technology stack during the phases of the Tech Stack
          Upgrade and Data & Functionality Migration.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card white shadow fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">What kind of support do you provide after the modernization is complete?</h3>
        <p class="body1">
          Our commitment does not stop once the project is done. On the contrary, we offer Ongoing Support for the
          continued optimal performance of your new system as your business grows.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card white shadow fade-from-bottom">
        <h3 class="heading3">
          What are the risks associated with modernizing a legacy system, and how do you mitigate them?
        </h3>
        <p class="body1">
          Again, to mitigate several risks, we implement a phased approach in such a way that, at each stage, the new
          system is tested.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <FinalEngagement
    title="Ready to Future-Proof Your Business?"
    description="Out with the Old, In with the New"
    buttonText="Book a Free Consultation"
  />
</MainLayout>
